oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Photograph of Lawrence Ray Estep
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Lawrence Ray Estep appears in his World War I uniform. He served in Recruit Co. 20, 5th Training Battn., 156th Depot Brigade before receiving a medical discharge for heart trouble in February 1918. Estep was from Giles County, Tennessee.
